",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"Usage Data:"}]," Agent proposals, execution logs, audit trails, and API interactions processed through the governance pipeline."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"Technical Data:"}]," IP addresses, browser type, device information, and access timestamps for security and operational purposes."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-white","children":"Analytics:"}]," Aggregated, anonymized usage statistics to improve the Service."]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"3. How We Use Your Information"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-slate-400","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Provide and maintain the governance platform"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Process agent proposals and maintain audit trails"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Send account-related communications"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Enforce policies and detect security threats"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Improve the Service based on usage patterns"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Comply with legal obligations"}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"4. Data Isolation"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Each tenant's data is logically isolated. Agent proposals, warrants, execution results, and audit logs belonging to one tenant are not accessible to other tenants. Audit trails are append-only and tamper-evident."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"5. Data Retention"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Audit trail data is retained for the duration of your account plus 7 years for compliance purposes. Account information is retained while your account is active. You may request deletion of your account data by contacting us, subject to legal retention requirements."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"6. Data Sharing"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We do not sell your data. We may share information with: (a) service providers who assist in operating the platform (hosting, email); (b) law enforcement when required by law; (c) in connection with a merger or acquisition."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"7. Security"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption in transit (TLS), encrypted storage, session management, and access controls. The warrant system provides cryptographic verification of all authorized executions."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"8. Your Rights"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"You have the right to: (a) access your personal data; (b) correct inaccurate data; (c) request deletion (subject to retention requirements); (d) export your data; (e) opt out of marketing communications."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"9. Cookies"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We use session cookies for authentication and minimal analytics cookies to understand site usage. We do not use advertising cookies or cross-site tracking."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-3","children":"10. Changes"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Material changes will be communicated via email or prominent notice on the Service. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"classNam